# Tailwind Design System

## Brand Colors (in tailwind.config.ts)
```
zapit-green: #0DC429     — primary CTAs, highlights, sticky call button
zapit-dark: #252525      — headings, dark sections
zapit-text: #333333      — body text
zapit-light: #f8f9fa     — section backgrounds
zapit-border: #e5e5e5    — dividers, card borders
white: #ffffff            — cards, overlays
```

## Typography
- Font: Roboto via `next/font/google` — never CDN link
- Headings: font-bold, tracking-tight
- H1: text-4xl md:text-5xl (42px desktop)
- H2: text-3xl md:text-4xl (36px)
- H3: text-xl md:text-2xl
- Body: text-base (16px), leading-relaxed
- Small: text-sm (13px)

## Spacing
- Section padding: py-16 md:py-24
- Container: max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8
- Card gap: gap-6 md:gap-8
- Stack spacing: space-y-4 or space-y-6

## Components
- Buttons: rounded-lg px-6 py-3, primary uses bg-zapit-green text-white
- Cards: rounded-xl border border-zapit-border bg-white shadow-sm
- Sticky Call Button: fixed bottom-4 right-4 z-50 bg-zapit-green rounded-full shadow-lg

## Mobile-First
- Always write mobile styles first, then add md: and lg: breakpoints
- Test at 375px width (iPhone SE) as minimum
- Navigation: hamburger on mobile, horizontal on desktop
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px
